title: Unorthodox plush pink makeup look
text: Is pink your favourite festive hue? Show your love for the soft, sensuous and feminine colour tone with this makeup look. Add some zing to your regular silver eyeshadow with a touch of pink and be festive-ready in no time. Pink and silver go hand in hand when one talks of beauty. Being glitzy and shimmering at the same time, this beauty look will make you a headturner in no time. It's simple, effective and oh-so-festive. Love it? Watch this tutorial and master the art of pink-silver eyes like a pro.
description: Add some zing to your regular silver eyeshadow with a touch of pink and be festive ready in no time.
